last_episode_to_air.overview: As chaos reigns, the Knights must convince Vera and Alyssa to work together to seal the eruption and save Lilith from the demon realm.

name: The Order
overview: Out to avenge his mother's death, a college student pledges a secret order and lands in a war between werewolves and practitioners of dark magic.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: College freshman Jack Morton joins a fabled secret society, The Order, where he is thrust into a world of magic, monsters and intrigue. As Jack goes deeper, he uncovers dark family secrets and an underground battle between werewolves and the magical dark arts.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: In season two, the lines between good and evil are more obscure than ever. The Knights struggle to regain their memories stolen from them by The Order and they crave retribution. But vengeance is hard to plan when you’re also fighting murderous magicians, strange cults and life-threatening demons. Does anyone even go to class anymore?

episodes.name: Hell Week (1)
episodes.overview: At Belgrave University, Jack pledges a secret society steeped in mystery and magic. Soon, a series of strange murders sets the campus on edge.

episodes.name: Hell Week (2)
episodes.overview: Pops shares a theory about the attacks. Jack and Alyssa try to keep an eye on the other pledges. At the Temple, Jack encounters a notorious figure.

episodes.name: Introduction to Ethics (1)
episodes.overview: Jack learns he's been selected for a rival secret society. Later, he gets a lesson in magic -- and discovers that every spell has a price.

episodes.name: Introduction to Ethics (2)
episodes.overview: Jack proposes an alliance with the Knights, and Randall teaches him how to harness his powers. Meanwhile, Edward takes Alyssa under his wing.

episodes.name: Homecoming (1)
episodes.overview: As the Order prepares to conduct a dangerous, sinister spell, the Knights enlist Jack to sabotage their plans.

episodes.name: Homecoming (2)
episodes.overview: While the Order hunts for werewolves on campus, Jack and Alyssa flee with Renee's necrophone, a tool used to communicate with the dead.

episodes.name: Undeclared (1)
episodes.overview: Alyssa confronts Jack about his secret. Headmistress Vera questions Edward about the Vade Maecum and sends Gabrielle on a truth-seeking mission.

episodes.name: Undeclared (2)
episodes.overview: Alyssa helps the Knights search for Randall and stumbles upon a doctor's twisted experiment. Edward is visited by the Vade Maecum's previous owner.

episodes.name: Finals (1)
episodes.overview: Consumed by ambition, Edward clashes with Vera -- and Alyssa is caught in the middle. Jack's brush with the Vade Maecum ignites a painful ordeal.

episodes.name: Finals (2)
episodes.overview: The Knights plot to thwart Edward's plan by kidnapping his son. Gabrielle and the Hermetic Counselor interrogate Lilith.

1.name: Season 1
1.overview: College freshman Jack Morton joins a fabled secret society, The Order, where he is thrust into a world of magic, monsters and intrigue. As Jack goes deeper, he uncovers dark family secrets and an underground battle between werewolves and the magical dark arts.

episodes.name: Free Radicals (1)
episodes.overview: After having the Knights' memories wiped, Vera plans to induct them into the Order. But her new pledges prove hard to control.

episodes.name: Free Radicals (2)
episodes.overview: While the Knights look for ways to protect themselves, Alyssa gives Jack a job: find the "magic tourist" who's been wreaking havoc on campus.

episodes.name: Fear Itself (1)
episodes.overview: The Knights raid the Order’s magic vault, Alyssa confides in Randall about her fading powers, and romance blooms between Lilith and Nicole.

episodes.name: Fear Itself (2)
episodes.overview: Vera leads the Order in a spell to summon Rogwan, a powerful demon. But when her plan goes awry, she needs the Knights on her side.

episodes.name: The Commons (1)
episodes.overview: Vera negotiates a deal with the Sons of Prometheus — a rival magic society — and sends Jack and Alyssa to their compound as hostages.

episodes.name: The Commons (2)
episodes.overview: Amid a standoff with the Prometheans, Alyssa goes into withdrawal. Meanwhile, Randall, Hamish and Gabrielle track professor Foley.

episodes.name: Spring Outbreak (1)
episodes.overview: The Knights weigh whether to join the Order. Alyssa suspects that her feelings for Jack might be blocking her magic. Kepler pulls rank on Vera.

episodes.name: Spring Outbreak (2)
episodes.overview: The Knights try to prevent a strange affliction from spreading. Kepler schemes to strip Vera of her power, and Alyssa searches Vera's house.

episodes.name: New World Order (1)
episodes.overview: Nicole finds a spell that could bring back Lilith, but it hinges on Alyssa’s cooperation. Jack tries to broker a deal between Vera and Salvador.

episodes.name: New World Order (2)
episodes.overview: As chaos reigns, the Knights must convince Vera and Alyssa to work together to seal the eruption and save Lilith from the demon realm.
